4.2. Priprava slozek na CM serveru a nahrani certifikatu s klicema
Na CM serveru pripravime strukturu slozek, kterou pote budem pouzivat pro ukladani CSR souboru, certifikatu, klicu a secretu.

create AutoTLS folders


ssh ${CM_Server}

mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/certs
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/keys
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/csr
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/scripts
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/archive
mkdir -p /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/.secret


# tree /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS
.
├── archive
├── certs
├── csr
└── keys


Po zalozeni slozek nahrajeme podepsane certifikaty do slozky certs - nazev certifikatu musi byt ve formatu - ${server_hostname}.crt a klic - ${server_hostname}.key

Dale vygenerujeme heslo k jks souborum do slozky secret:

generate password


# Generate truststore password
head -c 18 /dev/urandom | base64 > /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/.secret/truststore.pwd
# Generate keystore password
head -c 18 /dev/urandom | base64 > /opt/cloudera/AutoTLS/.secret/keystore.pwd
Tim mame pripravene vse co potrebujeme k zapnuti AutoTLS.

